:0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:03:36.000Z","msg":"有冇手足去宣傳下 叫人唔好報警"},{"pid":"2ec68743ef3c033d4cbbe19b32725302d8a9c255","tid":1544702,"uid":289116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:05:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>最後召集！</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">9月6號，全民戴裝日</span><br />\n<br />\n目的係提醒大家行街坐車都會隨時被襲擊，扑頭、噴椒、或身處毒霧環境，所以要戴上防具作象徵，靜默地抗議。<br />\n<br />\n以下幾點提議比番大家:<br />\n1. 番學番工放工時間做，[/red][/size=5]越多人做效果越好，人多亦唔易比人check身份證[size=5]<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n2. 行街坐車行商場都戴住，唔使怕奇怪，因為更無理既事日日都發生緊<br />\n3. 番工裝扮未必帶到頭盔，但唔戴都帶住，作為一個象徵，又或者只帶<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[red]口罩眼罩</span></span><br />\n4. 真勇武就小心，比人check身份證留record就麻煩<br />\n5. 只帶防具，只係要保護自己，唔好有其他可疑裝備<br />\n<br />\n[/gold][/size=6]當人人都有頭盔口罩係身既時候，就可以淡化帶gear本身既奇怪，保護大家，亦比一份支持勇武。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n<br />\n真係最後召集啦<br />\n幫手推<br />\n幫手share <br />\n最緊要一齊做<br />\n<br />\n俾所有人知道<br />\n[size=6][gold]<strong>五大訴求 缺一不可</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>抗爭未完架！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4b60444921d47272149ca1bd8685059727756f17","tid":1544702,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:06:45.000Z","msg":"點"},{"pid":"48656e2428c38bad25f6d78838cbbbda9cfc1d7f","tid":1544702,"uid":267304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:07:09.000Z","msg":"宜家咩情況？"},{"pid":"d124bf208c1f9c3c1745b2c401d33a60837d5205","tid":1544702,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:09:20.000Z","msg":"咩環境？"},{"pid":"fec736ed34a85919ce071b20cf55d5e32bee572e","tid":1544702,"uid":219488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif